    <div class="body">
        <p>The Zend_Db test suite does not run incubator-specific test components when run from within the incubator/tests directory. A number of E_NOTICE lines are output suggesting that the trunk version of the test configuration file is being loaded before the incubator version and even stub files creating within the incubator are not being called.</p>

